{"4483290": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "尋她：出租屋的秘密", "steam_appid": 4483290, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這是一款以 <strong>尋物探索與解謎</strong> 為核心玩法的 <strong>劇情驅動型遊戲</strong>。<br>玩家將扮演一名房東，在出租的房屋中逐漸發現一連串隱藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兩位性格截然不同的姐妹搬進了你的房子。隨著時間推移，你開始在房間中發現越來越多被遺落的物品與隱藏的線索。透過探索每個角落、解開謎題並收集關鍵道具，你將逐步揭開她們背後的故事。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >環境探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索房屋內的多個房間與場景，尋找隱藏的物品與線索。<br>許多重要道具被巧妙地隱藏在環境細節之中，需要玩家仔細觀察才能發現。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/1ceaf2bb565deb0d8b421dff5a42b40d.poster.avif?t=1773277918\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/1ceaf2bb565deb0d8b421dff5a42b40d.webm?t=1773277918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/1ceaf2bb565deb0d8b421dff5a42b40d.mp4?t=1773277918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/263a01d3a0349a1b6dda765fb7334c93.poster.avif?t=1773277918\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/263a01d3a0349a1b6dda765fb7334c93.webm?t=1773277918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483290/extras/263a01d3a0349a1b6dda765fb7334c93.mp4?t=1773277918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite